name: Fever Dream
description:
A piece inspired by a photograph I took during the winter in my own backyard, of the wild peach tree that is now full of leaves again, and beginning to bear fruit. It features the same white-haired character from “Waiting”. The electric pink colours combined with the surrealistic and unnatural vibe reminded me of the feeling of having a bad fever and the discomfort and feeling of being disconnected from reality that can come with it.
